# Disabling parsing If for some reason you don’t want to automatically parse the field ID and/or the categorical codes, you can explicitly set the keys name and/or replace_values to None. For example,

``` {

# …

“1558-0.0”:{

“name”: None, “replace_values”: None,

},

# …

}¶

will leave the column untouched: | 1558-0.0 | |----------| | 2 | | 5 | | 4 | | 4 | | 1 | | 6 | | … |
